==English==

===Alternative spellings===
* '''-sson''' (from -'s son)

===Etymology===
From Nordic [[patronym|patronyms]] of the form ''name'' + [[son]]

===Pronunciation===
* [[Wiktionary:Pronunciation_key|IPA]]: /sən/

===Suffix===
'''-son'''
# Added to a stem (usually a [[given name]] or [[surname]]) to form a [[patronymic]] [[surname]]

